w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_blackcountrynewroad_eddiewhelan_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-country-new-road">黑乡村，新路</a>分享了他们的新单曲“ Besties”，并确认了他们的新专辑“ Forever Howlong”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/black-country-new-road-ants-from-up-there-review-3149019">黑国，新路 - “从那里的蚂蚁”评论：雄伟，浪漫的独立摇滚</a></strong></li></ul><p>在乐队最近分享了“好朋友”的简短片段，并使用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-country-new-road-announce-new-single-besties-and-tease-new-album-with-interactive-billboards-across-london-3831772">伦敦各地的互动广告牌</a>来嘲笑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/black-country-new-road-ants-from-up-there-review-3149019">“蚂蚁从那里的蚂蚁”</a>的后续片段之后。</p><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-ford">詹姆斯·福特（James Ford）</a>制作的新专辑将于4月4日在Ninja Tune上发行，可以<a href="https://bcnr.lnk.to/forever-howlongPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预先保存。它将采用各种格式，包括在再生黑色乙烯基上的标准2XLP，这是由乐队签名的白色标签2XLP，一种独家的负面效果Artworked 2xlp，收藏家的版本2xLP，具有替代的Commellate Eco Jazz Red和Collector&#39;s Edition的替代跟踪列表录音带，还带有备用曲目列表。</p><p>您可以在下面收听的“好友”附有一个新视频，该视频将于GMT下午5点首映，然后与乐队进行现场问答。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：好朋友" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/4vzxEXWrTCI4AZQJ3x8gy1?go=1&#038;referral=labelaffiliate&#038;utm_source=oembed&#038;utm_medium=Merlin_ninja-tune&#038;utm_campaign=labelaffiliate&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=606af1abdc544d1b"></iframe></p><p>在谈到视频时，导演瑞安娜·怀特（Rianne White）曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">年轻的父亲</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">奥罗拉（Aurora）</a>合作，他说：“&#39;besties&#39;以一种感情舞进入了我的世界，这是一种理解的概念，探索了围绕世界的核心情感，并且它再次与她在一起的障碍。</p><p> “与乐队一起建立这一点，使我获得了许多回忆，从我的童年写信和地图到我的好朋友的一系列经验，以制定我们自己的地图和滑动门的叙述，并以本能和直觉的直觉和直觉：“我现在需要和我的好朋友在一起”。”</p><p>怀特继续说：“与佐治亚州[Ellery]，May [Kershaw]和Tyler [Hyde]合作，尤其是他们的表演中的一种真正的享受，从字面上看，与Charlie [Charlie [Charlie [Charlie&#39;&#39;的时刻相比，与Charlie [韦恩]，刘易斯[埃文斯]和卢克[马克]。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="黑国，新路 - “好朋友”（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cae57TpoyZg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在新专辑中，Ellery说：“它为专辑创造了一个真实的唱片，有三个女孩唱歌。由于女性的观点，这绝对与“从那里的蚂蚁”截然不同 - 我们所做的音乐也称赞。”</p><p>新闻稿还补充说，这张专辑是“一张雄心勃勃，精心详细的唱片，其中包括从巴洛克流行音乐到prog的所有内容以及Alt-Rock的触摸 - 从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joanna-newsom">Joanna Newsom</a>到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/randy-newman">Randy Newman</a>通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fiona-apple">Fiona Apple</a>和Janis Ian的所有事物 -然而，一直保留只有这种音乐家才能提出的那种明确的独特声音。”</p><p>该乐队还将在9月11日在诺丁汉的洛克城（Rock City）开幕的一系列英国，爱尔兰和欧洲巡回演出，然后于10月31日在O2 Academy Brixton结束。</p><p>可以<a href="https://bcnr.lnk.to/forever-howlongPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在下</a>周二（2月4日）下午3点在GMT之前预订其新专辑，从而为他们的英国和爱尔兰巡回演唱会购买预售门票。然后将通过电子邮件发送代码，并可以在第二天（2月5日） <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblack-country-new-road-tickets%2Fartist%2F5308878">在</a>GMT上购买票。</p><p>门票将于下周五（2月7日）在格林尼治标准时间上午10点进行一般销售，可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblack-country-new-road-tickets%2Fartist%2F5308878" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFcpNwRNxAY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.11